rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0001
rows.name: They're...all...dead. You killed them all...in cold blood...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0002
rows.name: Fortune did not smile upon them today.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0004
rows.name: You filthy Earth aliens do not belong on this planet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0005
rows.name:
You seem more fluent than the others.
Are you in charge?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0007
rows.name:
I command this squad, Earth alien.
Now it is time for you to surrender.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0009
rows.name:
I am called Elma. And I command THIS squad.
If this planet is your home, we apologize for intruding.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0010
rows.name:
We crash-landed here after our ship was damaged
in an attack by unknown adversaries.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0011
rows.name:
We were hoping we could negotiate
a peaceful settlement in exchange for our friends, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0012
rows.name:
Peaceful settlement?
Your words are wasted on us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0013
rows.name: All we can promise Earth aliens is a swift death![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0015
rows.name: Right. We triedâ€”looks like survival of the fittest it is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0016
rows.name: Fine then. Seeing as you know we come from Earth...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs03050100_MSG0017
rows.name:
I'm guessing there's a good chance
we might have a score to settle with you anyway.[ST:wait ]
